name: Bad Karma
description: You're being looked at differently these days; you have a reputation for being pitiless.

name: DIY freak
description: By making 100 upgrades you have shown you are as efficient as a factory!

name: Champion!
description: So, now you're the free combat champion of the arena on Mars!
lockedDescription: Complete the arena championship at the Curiosity's.

name: Treason
description: After having loyally served Abundance, you had to flee Ophir or face arrest...

name: On the run
description: You really are having trouble settling down: you also had to leave Noctis.

name: The fall
description: You managed to bring down Viktor and you've set out for the pole...

name: Hello, Earth?
description: You finally found the beacon, but you'll just have to settle for Mars from now on...

name: Best friend
description: You have solved all of your companions' problems; they couldn’t have hoped for a better friend!
lockedDescription: Finish all of the companion quests.

name: Grand Master of the secret
description: You've understood only too well that truth and power are not always the best of bedfellows...

name: Goodbye paradise.
description: You have decided to reveal the destruction of the Earth... Major upheavals lie in store...

name: Martian forever...
description: You have decided to reveal everything, and thus to be the architect of a new era.

name: Extreme survivor
description: You have finished The Technomancer in extreme mode; you are a true journeyman of the apocalypse!
lockedDescription: Finish the game on extreme difficulty.

name: Tough to beat
description: You have finished in hard mode; it would have taken more than just that to stop you...
lockedDescription: Finish the game on hard difficulty.

name: Traveler
description: You have finished The Technomancer in normal mode; now you're qualified for space travel!
lockedDescription: Finish the game on normal difficulty.

name: It's a secret
description: You guard a heavy secret, but now you are an officer in the Abundance army.

name: Obliging
description: Whatever your reasons, you have rendered service twenty times!

name: You have to start somewhere
description: It's only the beginning, but by upgrading your first skill you're on the right track!

name: Guardian
description: You are a peerless guardian; this type of combat holds no secrets for you.
lockedDescription: Unlock the entire guardian skill tree.

name: Rogue
description: You are slippery as an eel; you are expert at all thieving techniques!
lockedDescription: Unlock the entire rogue skill tree.

name: Technomancer
description: You create fluid at will; you are a true master of technomancy.
lockedDescription: Unlock the entire technomancer skill tree.

name: Warrior
description: Staff combat requires incredible discipline, and you have it down to perfection.
lockedDescription: Unlock the entire warrior skill tree.

name: Trapper
description: Nothing can beat you; you have carved up 100 creatures.

name: Sharpshooter
description: By hitting enemies 200 times with a pistol you have amply proven your shooting skills.
lockedDescription: Hit enemies 200 times using a pistol.

name: Like lightning
description: You've electrocuted enemies 200 times; it's effective but people are going to think you're sadistic.

name: Ace of staves
description: You have hit enemies 200 times with a staff; let's hope they've finally learned their lesson!
lockedDescription: Hit enemies 200 times using a staff.

name: Monster hunter
description: You have killed 60 creatures. Don't you ever think about protecting endangered species?

name: Lightweight
description: The 50 humanoids you took out find your technique elegant and very effective.

name: Middleweight
description: You have knocked out 100 humanoids; they feel you've been a bit heavy-handed.

name: Heavyweight
description: No one can doubt your ability to defeat your opponents now; not after 200 KOs.

name: Raider
description: You have dipped into 40 chests. After all, they weren't forced to leave stuff inside them...

name: The Godfather
description: Your alliance with the Vory has a brimstone odor to it, but the end surely justifies the means...

name: Noctis merchants
description: You are the ally of the Noctis merchants. Now those are friends you can surely count on.

name: Without fail
description: You have successfully parried 200 attacks with your shield; you really are hard to hit.

name: Opponents of the regime
description: No doubt a utopian sleeping inside of you; you have allied with the opponents of the regime.
lockedDescription: Ally with the opposition in Ophir.

name: A clockwork heart
description: You have succeeded in seducing Amelia; now you are ready to scour the tracks of Mars together.
lockedDescription: Enter into a romance with Amelia

name: Soulmate
description: You have discovered your soulmate in Andrew, and together you are enjoying the perfect love.
lockedDescription: Enter into a romance with Andrew

name: The spy who loved me
description: You have managed to melt Niesha's spying heart; now she will only have eyes for you.
lockedDescription: Enter into a romance with Niesha

name: With my captain
description: Soldier once, soldier forever: you have allied with the Abundance army.

name: Expert
description: You love digging deeper; you are a complete expert at a talent.
lockedDescription: Unlock the 3 levels of a talent

name: Burglar
description: Your light fingers have let you pick 50 locks.
